    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "You now render a markdown cell by 'executing' it - i.e. use one of the keyboard shortcuts like shift-enter, or click the play button at the top of the screen. This is deliberate - people editing documents with a lot of Markdown cells wanted to be able to keep several cells unrendered, so that text doesn't jump around as you're moving around the document.\n"
